    "prose_paragraphs": [
      "The most common asphalt-shingle install nationally is a gray in this exact tonal zone. Sierra Gray sits right inside that fairway: dark enough to feel anchored, light enough to keep the elevation breathing. The granule blend is engineered to read as a single quiet plane from the street.",
